{"tid":2428183,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★港股成交顯著縮減，較上個交易日減少34%","createTime":"2021-03-01T11:08:39.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-02T06:52:05.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e93ec5fe643b0eb87bab155e59752c196b833f51","tid":2428183,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T11:08:39.000Z","msg":"港股反彈超過470點，但成交顯著縮減，較上個交易日減少三成四。<br />\n<br />\n美國國債孳息率回落，美股期貨和區內股市造好，港股早段最多升570點，收市報29,452點，升472點，成交縮減至不足2,100億元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.tvb.com/finance/603cbb3134b0315a56025d75/%E6%B8%AF%E8%82%A1%E5%8F%8D%E5%BD%88%E9%80%BE470%E9%BB%9E-%E6%88%90%E4%BA%A4%E8%BC%83%E4%B8%8A%E5%80%8B%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E6%97%A5%E6%B8%9B34\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Ffinance%2F603cbb3134b0315a56025d75%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2582%25A1%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%25BD%2588%25E9%2580%25BE470%25E9%25BB%259E-%25E6%2588%2590%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E8%25BC%2583%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%2580%258B%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E6%2598%2593%25E6%2597%25A5%25E6%25B8%259B34&d=%2FJ3N9F3YYmWMkKlYGTVt18%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=42d198f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.tvb.com/finance/603cbb3134b0315a56025d75/%E6%B8%AF%E8%82%A1%E5%8F%8D%E5%BD%88%E9%80%BE470%E9%BB%9E-%E6%88%90%E4%BA%A4%E8%BC%83%E4%B8%8A%E5%80%8B%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E6%97%A5%E6%B8%9B34</a>"},{"pid":"80b6e60a301d726690b884ce4b057f33184c8395","tid":2428183,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T11:09:02.000Z","msg":"劏房effect<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d44ea44bdda467a164c12ee96ab45776c6c8920","tid":2428183,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T11:09:26.000Z","msg":"none buy<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15c3a874d643aeeefb47ca538d6961e157400649","tid":2428183,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T11:11:03.000Z","msg":"如果行情下跌時，某一段時間里成交量很大，這表示有大量股票從猶豫的投資者手裡，轉移到固執的投資者手裡。也就是說，如果成交量增加，行情仍然繼續下跌時，就是已經接近下一次上漲起點的信號。<br />\n<br />\n  當成交量小，且指數還繼續下跌時，就表示市場前景堪慮。相反地，當成交量愈來愈大，股票還不斷看漲時，也是前景堪慮。<br />\n<br />\n  當成交量小時，如果指數看漲，這種情形就非常有利。"},{"pid":"f232bf13d4992c372cf71cf6af5790dea9220a5d","tid":2428183,"uid":274732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T11:13:13.000Z","msg":"Tvb news?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcc83247f9b6834ea2bb47d606b3085d384b7dda","tid":2428183,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T04:42:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c31434d25b46bcf36e2dae853063fd9c39360c09","tid":2428183,"uid":223407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15c3a874d643aeeefb47ca538d6961e157400649","tid":2428183,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T11:11:03.000Z","msg":"如果行情下跌時，某一段時間里成交量很大，這表示有大量股票從猶豫的投資者手裡，轉移到固執的投資者手裡。也就是說，如果成交量增加，行情仍然繼續下跌時，就是已經接近下一次上漲起點的信號。<br />\n<br />\n  當成交量小，且指數還繼續下跌時，就表示市場前景堪慮。相反地，當成交量愈來愈大，股票還不斷看漲時，也是前景堪慮。<br />\n<br />\n  當成交量小時，如果指數看漲，這種情形就非常有利。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T05:46:15.000Z","msg":"吹大啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdd11597c9381886277bf8c2d0fbe02421a7de0d","tid":2428183,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-02T06:52:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />國際金融中心"}]}